PARAGON FIELD SERVICES, INC., Appellant(s)/Petitioner(s),
v.
KNIGHT CAPITAL FUNDING III, LLC, Appellee(s)/Respondent(s), CASE NO.: 3D17-2061 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Third District. DECEMBER 22, 2017

ORDERED that appellant's notice of voluntary dismissal of appeal is recognized by the Court, and this appeal from the Circuit Court for Miami-Dade County, Florida is hereby dismissed.
